</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>may be inaccurate or <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Neutral_point_of_view#Undue_weight" title="Wikipedia:Neutral point of view">unbalanced</a> in favor of certain viewpoints</b>. Please <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=History_of_science&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=History_of_science&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve the article</a> by adding information on neglected viewpoints, or discuss the issue on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:History_of_science" title="Talk:History of science">talk page</a>.</td>
