<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Islamic_MedText_c1500.jpg" class="image" title="15th century manuscript of Avicenna's The Canon of Medicine."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6d/Islamic_MedText_c1500.jpg/150px-Islamic_MedText_c1500.jpg" width="150" height="217" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Islamic_MedText_c1500.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
